Description




Beijing E-hualu Information Technology Co., Ltd., formerly BEIJING E-HUALU INFO TECHNOLOGY CO., LTD is a China-based company principally engaged in the development and distribution of smart traffic management platform systems and software. The Company operates through three main segments: Intelligent Traffic Management System Engineering segment, Public Security System Engineering System segment and Intelligent City System Engineering segment. The Company is primarily involved in the provision of information system integration services, system engineering services, technological advisory services and sales of products.


