Summary for Beijing E-Hualu Info Technology Co.,Ltd
BEIJING E-HUALU INFO TECHNOLOGY CO., LTD is principally engaged in the development and distribution of smart traffic management platform systems and software. The Company primarily provides urban transportation management systems, including advanced traffic management systems (ATMSs), integrated information management platforms, smart urban traffic control systems (UTC), smart expressway inlet and outlet control systems (EIC), smart traffic enforcement surveillance systems (TES), smart dynamic peccancy capture systems (DPC), smart traffic flow management systems (TFM), smart traffic close-circuit television (CCTV) and large screen display systems, among others, as well as mobile police systems, smart advanced traffic information systems and other systems.


