Company Description                    




                        Beijing E-Hualu Information Technology Co., Ltd., founded in April 2001, is a holding company owned by China Hualu Group Co., Ltd.. As a state-holding high-tech enterprise, E-Hualu is oriented toward the application of intelligent transportation systems (ITS) and specializing in core software development, data mining and decision support, intelligent transport and professional security products as well as systems integration and operational services. It has a registered capital of RMB50 million, a 300 personnel staff, 120 software products registered by the National Copyright Bureau and many project achievements throughout the country.                    


